                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6178" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0946</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7750 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">疫情下的困境——WX铜业副产品对主产品的桎梏</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Dilemma under the epidemic—the by-product of  WX copper industry constraints on the main product</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">姚文英</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新疆财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新疆五鑫铜业有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">矿冶业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">副产品；利益相关者；副产品产品管理；财务管理应急体系</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">By-product; Stakeholder; By-product management; Financial management emergency system</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020年新冠疫情来势汹汹，一时之间席卷了全国各地。为控制疫情而采取的全面封城措施，使得我国的经济受到了重创，在此疫情期间大部分企业遭到物流受阻、业绩受损、库存积压、供应链断裂等影响。大多数的企业在日常经营中往往侧重于对主产品的管理，忽视了副产品管理的重要性，也正是由于此次疫情的出现，才出现了较为少见的副产品对主产品的桎梏的一幕。此外，疫情的突然到来，企业拥有一套完整可行的应急财务管理体系的重要性也凸显出来，否则难以应对危机，很容易击溃企业的内部资金管理机构和程序，产生财务问题。本案例描述了WX铜业在受到新冠疫情的冲击之后，物流受阻，副产品难以及时销售又无处储存从而制约了主产品的生产等出现的一系列问题，虽然WX铜业采取了相关措施来缓解此问题，但也引发了企业管理人员对于加强副产品产品管理以及建立一套完整可行的应急财务管理体系的深刻思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The COVID-19 is menacing and sweeping across the country for a while. In order to control the spread of the epidemic, most areas in China have taken comprehensive measures to close cities. However, China&#39;s economy has been hit hard, during the epidemic period, most enterprises were affected by logistics, performance damage, inventory overstocking, supply chain disruption and so on. Most enterprises often focus on the management of the main products in their daily operations, ignoring the importance of by-product management. It is precisely because of the emergence of the epidemic, there is a relatively rare scene of by-products shackling the main product. In addition, the sudden arrival of the epidemic, the enterprise has a complete set of feasible emergency financial management system is also highlighted, otherwise it is difficult to deal with the crisis, it is easy to destroy the enterprise&#39;s internal capital management institutions and procedures, resulting in financial problems.although the epidemic has been effectively controlled under this environment.This case describes the impact of COVID-19 in WX copper industry, logistics is hampered, by-products are difficult to sell in time and there is no place to store, thus restricting the production of the main products. Although Enterprise A has taken a series of measures to alleviate this problem, it also let the enterprise managers realize the importance of establishing a complete and feasible emergency financial management system and strengthen the by-product, joint product management.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》、《管理学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务管理、风险管理与应对</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
